text: WCHL may refer to: * Western Canada Hockey League (1921–26) * Western Canada Hockey League (1932–33) (minor pro) * Worcester Collegiate Hockey League (1966–72) (second-tier NCAA) * Western Hockey League (1968–78), also known as the Western Canada Hockey League * West Coast Hockey League (1995–2003) * Western Collegiate Hockey League (2013–) * WCHL (AM), a radio station licensed to Chapel Hill, North Carolina, United States
